race.comment: SOMEWHERE SOON (10) was a big improver second-up here when launching a strong late bid to get within a length of the winner. Peaking now and can go a couple better with fresh legs. HEAD OF THE HERD (2) has mixed his form this time in but is a track and trip winner here and finally draws a good gate. Crowther's booking shows stable confidence. TOFINO (7) backs up quickly after a moderate effort at Gawler. Was a brave winner over the track and trip two back. Keeping safe. MORLAIX (8) is In a suitable race and should be in the mix.
